      "title": "Code from custom node",
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "## Code: KSampler in Isolation\n\n### Custom Node (`nodes/nodes_z_image_turbo.py`)\n\n```python\nclass KSampler_ZIMG(io.ComfyNode):\n    @classmethod\n    def execute(cls, model, seed, steps,\n                cfg, sampler_name, scheduler,\n                positive, negative,\n                latent_image, denoise):\n        # All of this runs in the child\n        # process. model is a proxy.\n        noise = comfy.sample.prepare_noise(\n            latent_samples, seed, batch_inds\n        )\n        samples = comfy.sample.sample(\n            model,   # ModelPatcherProxy\n            noise, steps, cfg,\n            sampler_name, scheduler,\n            positive, negative,\n            latent_samples,\n            denoise=denoise,\n            ...\n        )\n        return io.NodeOutput(out)\n```\n\n### What Happens During Sampling\n\nEach denoising step triggers:\n1. Child calls `model.apply_model(x, t)` on proxy\n2. Proxy sends RPC to host with CUDA IPC tensor handles\n3. Host executes real model forward pass on GPU\n4. Host returns result tensor via CUDA IPC\n5. Child receives zero-copy tensor reference\n\n### Key Isolation Files\n\n- `comfy/isolation/runtime_helpers.py` — stub class dispatch\n- `comfy/isolation/extension_wrapper.py` — child-side execution\n- `pyisolate/_internal/tensor_serializer.py` — CUDA IPC\n"
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#000"
